description: Welcome to 283 Bowen Street! Beautiful penthouse on a quiet one-way street just steps from Broadway's best restaurants and night life. This open layout concept with ample outdoor space is perfect for entertainers. Come check out the most affordable two bed two bath with parking on the market.
